cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a new modeling approach that combines the advantages of both generative and discriminative models. It is evaluated on a classification task with artificial data and a semantic image segmentation problem, indicating its relevance to machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural networks (cs.NE).
